Bell Labs

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Bell Telephone Laboratories)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For buildings named Bell Telephone Laboratories, see Bell Laboratories Building (Manhattan).

Nokia Bell Labs


Bell Labs logo since Nokia's acquisition in 2016.




Bell Laboratories in Murray Hill, New Jersey




Type

Subsidiary of Nokia


Industry
