07/14/2016

Scott T.

Scott T.



    My wife and I have sent our children - currently ages 4-and-a-half and 6 months - to School Bell two days/week since they've been alive. About six child care centers exist within a 5-mile radius...
    






  
  
            <p>School Bell Early Childhood Education Center provides learning programs for kids ages 6-weeks to 12-years-old. It is located in a brick schoolhouse building on the east side of John R. Rd., just south of East South Blvd. Among its academic program offerings are a variety of creative lessons, including dance and gymnastics. Before and after school programs are available for older children, as well as summer camps.</p>
          






















